  <ul>
    <li><p class='lead'>You click Approve or Disapprove.</p></li>
    <li><p class='lead'>We save your vote in the database.</p></li>
    <li><p class='lead'>We show the proportion of votes for the previous 24-hour window.</p></li>
    <li><p class='lead'>You are allowed to vote once every day.</p></li>
